BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (SCREEN TIME TOKEN SYSTEM) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (Cut out tokens below. Kids earn tokens for good behavior and can 'spend' them on screen) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.0 Td (time. Makes it tangible and teaches budgeting!) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 648.2 Td (HOW IT WORKS:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 632.2 Td (1. Child earns tokens for: chores, reading, kindness, outdoor play) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 618.2 Td (2. Each token = 15 minutes of screen time) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 604.2 Td (3. Child decides WHEN to spend tokens \(teaches self-regulation!\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 590.2 Td (4. Unspent tokens at end of week = bonus reward!) Tj ET
