stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (FAMILY MEETING: DIGITAL WELLNESS DISCUSSION) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (Use these questions for a monthly family check-in about screens:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 666.2 Td (   1. What's your favorite thing to do that doesn't involve a screen?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 642.4 Td (   2. How do you feel AFTER a long time on screens? \(tired? wired? sad?\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 618.6 Td (   3. Is there anything you've seen online that confused or upset you?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 594.8 Td (   4. What would you do with an extra hour if screens weren't an option?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 571.0 Td (   5. Do you think our family rules about screens are fair? What would you change?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 547.2 Td (   6. What's one new hobby or skill you'd like to try?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 523.4 Td (   7. How can we help each other put screens down?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 499.6 Td (   8. What's the best part of our screen-free time together?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 475.8 Td (   9. Is anyone at school talking about things they see online? How does that feel?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 452.0 Td (  10. What 'screen-free challenge' should our family try this week?) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
