<< /Length 1740 >>
stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (PARENT TIPS: MAKING THIS WORK) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 676.2 Td (THE FIRST WEEK \(Expect pushback!\):) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 660.2 Td (- Announce new system at a family meeting - get input) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 646.2 Td (- Start on a weekend when everyone is calm) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 632.2 Td (- Expect 2-3 days of complaints - stay consistent) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 618.2 Td (- Celebrate EVERY day they follow the system) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 604.2 Td (- Lead by example - limit YOUR screen time too!) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 576.4 Td (WHEN THEY PUSH BACK \(and they will\):) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 560.4 Td (Say: 'I understand you're frustrated. The rules still apply.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 546.4 Td (Say: 'You can earn more screen time by [specific task].') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 532.4 Td (Say: 'What from the 100 activities list sounds fun right now?') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 518.4 Td (Don't say: 'Because I said so!' \(explain the WHY\)) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 490.6 Td (SIGNS THE SYSTEM IS WORKING:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 474.6 Td ([ ] Less arguing about screen time) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 460.6 Td ([ ] Child asks for activities instead of screens) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 446.6 Td ([ ] Better sleep \(falling asleep faster\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 432.6 Td ([ ] More creativity and independent play) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 418.6 Td ([ ] Child self-regulates \(turns off without being told\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 404.6 Td ([ ] More family conversation and connection) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 380.8 Td (Remember: Progress > Perfection. Even 30% less screen time = better outcomes.) Tj ET
54 360.8 m 558 360.8 l 0.5 w S
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 350.8 Td (By Daniel Tesfamariam | Raising humans, not screen zombies.) Tj ET
endstream
